Package: rpart.translator
Type: Package
Title: Tool for Simplifying Decision Trees into Table Readable Format
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jason", "Wittenauer", email = "jasonwi1202@gmail.com", role = "cre"), 
    person("Justin", "Silva", email = "justinsilva@hotmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: A tool for formating a rpart decision tree model into a table of rules and subrules. The table is in a database friendly format to provide transparency into the model decision making process.
